headline: Deckers Outdoor (NYSE:DECK) Launches New UGG速? Clog Collection In Mustard Seed Colorway
summary: Deckers Outdoor (NYSE:DECK) introduced its Goldenstar and Goldencoast UGGbraid Clog collection this past week, engaging its customer base with innovative products and a creative promotional event in partnership with Gray's Papaya.
